          <source>If <bpt id="p1">*</bpt>hdc<ept id="p1">*</ept> is not <bpt id="p2">**</bpt>NULL<ept id="p2">**</ept> and <ph id="ph1">`ptd`</ph> is <bpt id="p3">**</bpt>NULL<ept id="p3">**</ept>, the function returns the existing <bpt id="p4">*</bpt>hdc<ept id="p4">*</ept>.</source>
